pullrequest.title: Model submission for X5 (Teambase) sensor configuration 1 from Sophisticated Engineering.

content.raw: The main reason for using this “Teambase” instead of using a X3 config 1 is expected much lower costs. \(In the Tunnel circuit we used a X3 config 1.\) Additionally it is expected that the Teambase will have unlimited Battery time and no risk of failure.
